Additional Note		
In case of carpet area of booked inventories and unit consideration for booked and unbooked inventories are as certified by the promotor.	
Coherence		
    1	The architect certificate is formatted in a such a way that entire work is bifurcated into various activities and architech is required to cerfity percentage of work completion of such activities  The architect certificate does not provide overall percentage of work completed of the project  This being a technical matter we are not in a position to comment upon whether physical work completed as per architect certificate is in coherence with acutal expenditure incurred and paid
    2	Difference up to 10 percentage  between expenditure incurred as per Engineer certificate vis a vis expenditure incurred as per books of account is considered as physical work completed is in coherence with actual expenditure incurred and paid
